apihelp-parser-migration-summary: Analysar le syntaxe de un pagina con duo configurationes differente del analysator syntactic.
apihelp-parser-migration-param-title: Le titulo del pagina a cargar e analysar.
apihelp-parser-migration-param-config: Le configuration del analysator syntactic a usar. Pote esser "old" (ancian), "new" (nove), o "old|new".
apihelp-parser-migration-param-redirect: Le redirectiones es sequite per predefinition. Usa "no" pro non sequer redirectiones.
